Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是什么啊  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟我的计算一致的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体之后的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够与Alone对抗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  能够打倒Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船舰被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体之后去拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是那么厉害的事情我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果期望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万事俱备只欠东风了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做  我想跟小茜一起拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界唯一的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小葵的钥匙哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要动手咯  作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Texture ON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也变身成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小岛被…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢下手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
