Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会赔偿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  完美的本垒打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都被别人保护的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就能战斗了  和小茜一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.95,Disp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,289)}示现引擎系统管理中心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,示现引擎被某物体强行吸收了大量能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必惊慌  恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统被强制入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊  一色老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久违了啊  紫条君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微借用下引擎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和老师您说的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我们如果能相信老师所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是后悔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是战斗的时候  紫条君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船务长  那个看起来像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连导弹都不起作用的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却被飞在空中的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是示现引擎管理局的紫条
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为这里的全权负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向负责保卫Blue Island的所有人下令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在大家正因为看到现实中不可能存在的东西而震惊着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只有一件事非常肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是  那些少女们才拥有对抗我们的敌人Alone的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽全力掩护她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的未来都寄托在她们身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Rang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我来保护大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯独这里情况不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  瞄准那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone  能量反应急剧下降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活动停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样给它最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(354,329)}Docking Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始咯  合体作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘亲下小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？亲亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是亲额头啦  额头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有什么流进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看见小葵的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看见小茜的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  合体不了啊  坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩听好  我知道失败的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  能立即修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体的瞬间  作战所需的能量朝负方向增长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们中的一人无意识中在拒绝合体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说失败的原因在于你们之间的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.46,Disp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,289)}二年前·伊豆大岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  爸爸你们什么时候来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  葵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时是来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是医生也说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里疗养对身体是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加油恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没打到你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  你喜欢番茄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个  不介意的话就吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说啊  这很甜超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  你住在这里啊  好棒的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的番茄  非常的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  希望你能告诉我在哪儿买的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次再带来给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个番茄是我家田里种出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫一色茜  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵  我叫做二叶葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教了  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说不能合体是我们的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说了事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是事实  要是我们不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这世上肯定就没人能合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要合体的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像小茜要融入进来一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  合体的话  会共有相互的记忆和意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我以为你们没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会有问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你难道能确信自己没对对方隐瞒什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真够烦的  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那我再去检查下程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小葵  就先这样做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的话一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone再次开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量干涉增大  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破极限  无法侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  和刚才的能量完全不是一个等级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Palette Suits已经不是它的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Rang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Impact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一直都在对你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到合体时这个谎言会被揭穿我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…其实最讨厌吃番茄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是又想要和小茜交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明吃都不吃却还说番茄好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不能合体的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错  真的很对不起  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃饭的时候如果有番茄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会露出非常讨厌的表情吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很明显的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为了不让我失望而努力吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(442,330)}Vivid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一这样想  我就好像这样  充满干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我和小葵能永远永远都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能成为至交的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵是我最要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  我们合为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Blue Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Impact
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全限制  解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎出力  120%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,150%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破临界  出力200%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Final Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算是  度过危机了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  这只是开始  紫条君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌上我们未来的战斗的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被妨碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  送报纸一休息就睡懒觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天和邪恶的怪兽打得精疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是听爷爷说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我真的好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个还会再出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后姐姐还要再战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为他说只有我们才能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不能一起战斗呢  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦  合体
